  "title": "Quantity Surveyor/Assistant Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u><br /><br />1.     Taking off quantites<br />2.     Study contract documents / drawings and raise queries for clarifications<br />3.     Prepare and review quotations<br />4.     Obtain quotation, liaise and negotiate with sub-contractor and supplier<br />5.     Prepare variation order from on-going project and submit to client<br />6.     Familiar with Singapore Contracts<br />7.     Salary offer will depends on experience and qualifications</p><p><u><strong>Job Requirement</strong></u></p><p>1.     Diploma in Quantity Surveying<br />2.     Must have relevant experience in GeBiz<br />3.     Proficient in all Microsoft Office & Adobe Acrobat <br />4.     Proficient in Autocad will be great advantages<br />5.     Able to work independently & Willing to learn <br />6.     5 Days Work Week</p>",
